data.description: Open House, Sunday, 9/25, from 2 PM - 4 PM! Welcome home to this well maintained all brick ranch in highly sought after Stonybrooke neighborhood! This home features the perfect open floor plan with vaulted ceilings in the great room with a warm and cozy woodburning fireplace! Gorgeous hardwood floors throughout! Open kitchen concept has two dining areas with tons of natural light pouring in! Three bedrooms and two full baths! The primary bedroom with en-suite bathroom features a spa jacuzzi tub, massive walk in closet, and great walk in shower! Sitting on an enormous lot with plenty of backyard space and a private deck off the kitchen for you to enjoy! Functionality at its finest with laundry mudroom space off of the two car attached garage! The huge basement is perfect for storage and waiting to be finished for double the square footage! New roof in 2021! New flooring in 2017! Call today for a private showing before this home is SOLD!
